# Add `permite_conciliar` column to `cuentas` table

The goal is to add a boolean column `permite_conciliar` to the `cuentas` table to control which accounts can be reconciled.

## User Review Required
> [!IMPORTANT]
> The database schema will be modified. A new column `permite_conciliar` (BOOLEAN, default FALSE) will be added to the `cuentas` table.

## Proposed Changes

### Database Schema
An `ALTER TABLE` script will be executed.

#### [NEW] [add_permite_conciliar_column.py](file:///f:/1.%20Cloud/4.%20AI/1.%20Antigravity/ConciliacionWeb/add_permite_conciliar_column.py)
